Package: uscore
Type: Package
Title: Computes empirical rank-based scores
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Vincenzo", "Coia", email = "vincenzo.coia@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Calculates uniform scores from a vector of numeric values, 
    essentially fitting the values equally between 0 and 1. These values
    can take on Normal distribution spacing, or return period spacing.
